- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses probabilistic latent variable models, which are a type of machine learning. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses generative models, which are a type of AI. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses controlling attributes of speech, which could be seen as a type of control system.
